<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<h3 id="theme">Theme</h3>
<p>In order to give a background color to a callout, use a <a href="/design/color#utilities">background utility class</a> and a <code>data-theme</code> attribute with the value <code>light</code> or <code>dark</code>. This will also take care of coloring for foreground elements automatically.</p>

{% embed "@tch/includes/example.twig" with {
  line_highlight: "1",
} %}
{% block content %}
