<h3 id="full-bleed-only">Full-bleed only</h3>
<p>If you wish to achieve the &quot;full bleed&quot; effect without a background color or additional spacing, you can use the <code>.full-bleed</code> utility class. The below example demonstrates its use with an image.</p>

